          </mj-text>
          <mj-text padding-top="10px">See the <a
              href="https://bugs.sogo.nu/changelog_page.php?version_id=253">closed tickets</a> for this release and
            the complete <a href="https://github.com/Alinto/sogo/compare/SOGo-5.8.2...SOGo-5.8.3">change log</a>.
          </mj-text>
          <mj-button padding-top="40px" padding-bottom="0" href="https://www.sogo.nu/download.html#/v5">Download
          </mj-button>
